comment: Temple (WAS) makes slight contact to the body with Johnson (MIA) as he goes up for the putback, but the contact does not affect his shot attempt.

After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that the ball was inside the cylinder when touched by Johnson (MIA) is incorrectly overturned and the basket is counted. After the initial legal tap, there is a subsequent illegal tap inside the cylinder.
Beasley (MIA) does not dislodge Nene (WAS) with the contact in the post.
Pierce (WAS) makes slight contact with Walker's (MIA) hand after the ball is released, but it does not affect his ability to follow-through.
Johnson (MIA) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
Napier (MIA) commits a take foul on Beal (WAS).
